# Group Provinces
Provinces can be accessed here
Provinces can have cities under them, and must be part of a Country 


## Provinces Collection [/provinces?include=includes&limit=limit]
+ Parameters
    + limit (optional, number, `1`) ... Numerical `limit` to apply to how many records are returned.
    + includes (optional, string, `'modifier'`) ... `includes` The relations that you want returned as part of the object. Options are: `modifier`, `country`, `cities, or `all`

